Program: The Why Factor
Title: Why Does Commuting Make us the Way we Are?
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p0343hhz
Last Broadcast Date: Mon 12 Oct 2015
Hundreds of millions of us bear the stress and boredom of the same journey day in day out - the commute. For some it is a time of reflection while for others it is a time to turn the air blue with howls of frustration. Why does commuting make us the people we are and how? (Photo: Rush hour traffic in Nairobi. Credit: Abdinoor Maalim) Show less